"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"在沙漠里，由于白天沙石被太阳晒得灼热，接近沙层的空气升高极快，形成了下层热上层冷的温度分布，造成下部空气密度远比上层空气温密度小的状况，这时前方景物的光线会由密度大的空间向密度小的空气折射，从而形成了下现蜃景，远远望去宛如水中倒影，在沙漠中长途跋涉的人，燥热干咳，看到下现蜃景常常会误认为达到了清凉湖畔，但是一阵风沙卷过，仍是一望无际的沙漠，这种景象只是一种幻象\",\"timestamp\":1642731193,\"title\":\"下现蜃景\"},\"digest\":\"hFuBDe1O9FJH9_qfnMF8vO1KY0SBko69JFjE6Upy_EE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf73f001E7B36302Cd9A8A9dDD6FDA0ec3EB5E4F4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"wf4qLTGEnnCFFO-HwX0UnAu1mLcDaSOOMpcuGx8K9XY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7cSF1nu5r1hSUa-XjholEZzmqnXQNAggTQT13JaTHbk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"9uOjh-XZWT9tBeQLkE2EivFIQOhfWWSlZvlkV74--GoKS2NJM1eIEJU5iCyO2--u6SA13JqmepaWgRuDzKcOfQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa9332667ac73fe897ff69f1d2cfc1d1369a1bdd0b5a7fd44042bc222b6542fad0c9e2b341614852c2c05028b9b36112ec579b21c0820edac4d667e8eb04006ca1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"wf4qLTGEnnCFFO-HwX0UnAu1mLcDaSOOMpcuGx8K9XY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7cSF1nu5r1hSUa-XjholEZzmqnXQNAggTQT13JaTHbk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"hFuBDe1O9FJH9_qfnMF8vO1KY0SBko69JFjE6Upy_EE\"}"